Sorry it took a bit to reply. I have taken a needed vacay from reality! The tones basically outline a C Major triad (C E G as 1, 3, 5). The triad is outlined or heard in its second inversion (the 1 6/4 inversion) so, it is 5 (G) up a Major 6th to 3 (E), then down a minor third to 1 (C). The repeated tone is a repeat of 1.
